---
title: Balsamic-Fig Chicken with Roasted Sweet Potatoes and Arugula Salad
description: We're big fans of pan sauces because they're a simple way to add extra flavour to dishes. Here, fig jam, balsamic vinegar, and fresh rosemary are allowed to mingle with the natural juices from the chicken to create a sweet and savoury condiment that you'll want to drizzle over everything.
